<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Backend در حال جوشیدن...</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: #0f2027; 
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #2c5364, #203a43, #0f2027);
        color: #fff;
        font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .pot {
        width: 200px;
        height: 150px;
        background: #444;
        border-radius: 0 0 100px 100px;
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        box-shadow: inset 0 20px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      .steam {
        position: absolute;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        top: -30px;
        left: 50%;
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: steam 2s infinite ease-in-out;
      }

      .steam:nth-child(2) {
        left: 40%;
        animation-delay: 0.5s;
      }

      .steam:nth-child(3) {
        left: 60%;
        animation-delay: 1s;
      }

      @keyframes steam {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(0) translateY(0) scale(1);
          opacity: 0.8;
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(-10px) translateY(-50px) scale(1.5);
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(10px) translateY(-100px) scale(0.5);
          opacity: 0;
        }
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px #000;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="pot">
      <div class="steam"></div>
      <div class="steam"></div>
      <div class="steam"></div>
    </div>
    <h1>🍲 ...Backend در حال جوشیدن</h1>
    <p>!...داریم بک اند رو با عشق می‌پزیم یه قهوه بگیر و برگرد</p>
  </body>
</html>
